Splunk Dashboard Monitoring
----------------------------------------
Author: Raj
Version/Date: 1.0/10-13-2016

Using this app:
----------------------------------------

ABOUT
------
This app is for splunk administrators to figure out who/what is responsible for slow splunk performance. This app provides the metrics around active search heads, apps, dashboards, users, historical and real-time searches. 


INSTALLATION
-------------
Install this app on Splunk search heads.
